Famous Nigerian rapper, M.I Abaga says his next album might earn him a Grammy award. The soon-to-wed rapper made this known as he announced he’s ready to focus on music. According to M.I, he is ready to focus on making music after his engagement announcement. Recall that M.I recently revealed the identity of his new lover as he announced marriage dates. He commended his fans for staying with him despite not releasing music in a long time. His tweet read, “And now that that is all over, my music coming soon. “Now I can focus so I release this album properly because it’s a classic. Might win a Grammy. I appreciate your patience.”